descriptionHtml:
نحن ملتزمون بتقديم وضمان افضل انواع الاطعمة للحيوانات الاليفة مع خبرة ليس لها مثيل فى الكويت سواء فى الطعام او فى نظافة الحيوانات

قامت ادارة Pet Point باطلاق تطبيق Pet Point للهواتف الذكية والذي نحرص به على سهولة الاستخدام والتصفح والطلب، حرصا منا على تقديم أفضل الخدمات لزبائننا.
شاكرين لكم ثقتكم بنا.

مميزات التطبيق:

- تصفح منتجات الخاصة بالحيوانات الأليفة.

- منتجات مقسمة حسب الفئات .

- قسم المنتجات حسب العلامات التجارية.

- عروض وخصومات على المنتجات.

- سهولة البحث عن طريق مربع البحث.

- سهولة التصفح عن طريق تصفية المنتجات أو الترتيب حسب الرغبة.

- أشعارات مخصصة داخل التطبيق.

- تسجيل للمستخدم

- امكانية الطلب مباشرة عن طريق التطبيق.

- متابعة طلباتي.

- الدفع مباشرة او عند التوصيل.

والعديد من المميزات داخل التطبيق لخدمتكم.

descriptionHtml:
Pet Point mobile app is the official online gateway for Pet Point Co. store located in Kuwait
that provides pet food, accessories, health products and all pet supplies as well as grooming services and deliver to all areas in Kuwait

Pet Point app has more than 30,000+ Products and more than 1000+ “Top Top” Brands

Pet point provides weekly and monthly offers and discounts through the app, you can order 24/7 and delivery will be in SAME DAY !!

The app is divided in several categories to make it easier for you where to find what you are looking for !

You can pay by KNET , Visa , MasterCard as well as Cash

You can search, filter and sort products based on their category, brand and price

You can follow up you order status as well as check your historical order list

We are excited to serve you

Pet point, ALL your pet supplies at one POINT !

Pet Point mobile app is the official online gateway for Pet Point Co. store located in Kuwait
that provides pet food, accessories, health products and all pet supplies as well as grooming services and deliver to all areas in Kuwait

Pet Point app has more than 30,000+ Products and more than 1000+ “Top Top” Brands

Pet point provides weekly and monthly offers and discounts through the app, you can order 24/7 and delivery will be in SAME DAY !!

The app is divided in several categories to make it easier for you where to find what you are looking for !

You can pay by KNET , Visa , MasterCard as well as Cash

You can search, filter and sort products based on their category, brand and price

You can follow up you order status as well as check your historical order list

We are excited to serve you
